title: Timeline
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

A timeline places events on a chronological axis. Use it for version history, project milestones, and historical context. ''New in Mermaid 9.4.''

---

!! Basic example

```
timeline
    title Plugin Version History
    2021 : v0.3.2 — Mermaid 8.x
    2022 : v0.3.7 — Mermaid 9.3
    2024 : v0.3.8 — TiddlyWiki 5.3.3
    2026 : v0.4.0 — Mermaid 11.14.0
```

$$$text/vnd.tiddlywiki.mermaid
