---

!! Syntax

```
timeline
    title My Timeline
    2020 : Event A
         : Event B (same period, second entry)
    section Next Phase
        2021 : Event C
```

* ''Period labels'' are free text — use years, quarters, sprint names, version numbers.
* ''Multiple events'' per period: indent additional `: event` lines under the same period.
* ''Sections'' group periods with a visual header. They are optional.

!! Tips

* Long event text wraps automatically.
* The `–` dash in period ranges is a display choice — the label is just text, not parsed.
* Sections help readability for timelines spanning many years.

